  "headline": "<h2>Gameplay</h2>", 
  "content": "<p>Count Jokula, the blood-sucking slot game offers players the chance to win big over three reels and five fixed paylines. With stakes ranging from €0.05 to €100 per spin, this game is perfect for players that are looking for a bite-sized betting experience. </p><p>The real star of the slot is the Joker Wild symbol which substitutes all high and low-paying symbols. It's so good that other symbols are just dying to get in contact with it. The Shapeshifter feature during the base game allows the bat symbol, usually a Halloween decoration, to randomly transform into a Joker Wild symbol, giving players even more chances to win. It's clear that even bats love the Joker Wild.</p><p>Count Jokula is the perfect game for those who love to sink their teeth into big wins. With all the features and potential for big payouts, players will feel like a king or queen of the undead. Don't be scared to spin those reels and see if Count Jokula is feeling generous enough to give you some golden garlic. </p>"
